---

{% submission %}

{% submission-part type="problem" %}

There are nearly 1000 science specific words that students need to learn. Teachers are over run with marking so we don't know how to test the words they need to know without adding to our workload. 

{% /submission-part %}

{% submission-part type="proposed-solution" %}

An app/ website specifically for key words. Including spellings, definitions and practice of putting the words into context e.g. gap full sentences. Thinking there can be lots of different topics, students can be set a topic for homework, complete the task online and then it will self mark and staff can look at the analytics and determine how long they spent doing it, what score they got and a break down of that score for spellings, definitions and sentences so that we can then target that area easily and help them to improve. Something similar to the website Seneca Learning I guess but specifically for science vocabulary! 

{% /submission-part %}

{% /submission %}